  "title": "Interior Designer #79978",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Furniture Wholesaler</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Interior Designer</strong></li><li>Working Location: East – Ubi (Walking distance from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days / Mon-Fri: 9am-6pm, Sat: 9am-1pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD3500</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Play a key role in transforming client visions into practical, stylish, and high-quality interiors</li><li>Understand client goals, requirements, and preferences.</li><li>Conduct site visits and prepare design briefs and proposals.</li><li>Conceptualise and develop design ideas, themes, and layouts.</li><li>Produce design drawings, mood boards, 3D visualisations, and material selections.</li><li>Ensure designs align with the company’s capabilities in furniture supply and renovation works.</li><li>Prepare detailed cost estimates, budgets, and project timelines.</li><li>Coordinate with contractors, suppliers, and vendors to ensure timely delivery and quality standards.</li><li>Oversee renovation and installation processes on-site.</li><li>Ensure design specifications, safety, and compliance standards are met.</li><li>Stay updated with the latest design trends, materials, and technologies.</li><li>Ensure compliance with Singapore’s building codes, regulations, and sustainability standards.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. ITE</li><li>Min 1 year of experience in interior design or renovation projects</li><li>Proficient in design software such as AutoCAD, SketchUp, 3ds Max, or Adobe Creative Suite</li><li>Strong knowledge of materials, furnishings, and lighting are a plus</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79978 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
